title: Ep.4: Giveaway Update, Packers Vs Steelers, Fury Vs Wilder 3, Seahawks Win, Heartbreaking Oregon Loss, and More.
description: 100 listener giveaway updates. TWO winners get a jersey of their choice from any sport, team, or player. Are the packers better than the steelers all around? Will the pac 12 be represented in the CFP any time soon? Tune in for another great episode.
